\newlabel{fig:bubble}{{7}{7}{Parity-preserving bubble region on the \ambibf {} tape. Gray cells (even index) form the bubble support $\Omega _k$. Drift arrows on exterior cells illustrate stochastic noise the bubble must survive}{figure.7}{}}
